<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <title>Update Email Instructions</title>
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px;">
    <table
      align="center"
      width="600"
      cellpadding="0"
      cellspacing="0"
      style="background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 6px; padding: 20px;"
    >
      <tr>
        <td style="font-size: 16px; color: #333333;">
          <p>You can change your account email to {@user.email} by visiting the link below:</p>

          <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
            <a
              href={@url}
              style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;"
            >
              Update Email
            </a>
          </p>

          <p>If you didn't request this change, please ignore this.</p>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
